    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.abs(v0)
    tmp = wp.abs(((v1 + 0.82 + v0 + 0.33) - wp.exp(v1 + 0.89)))
    v0 = wp.abs(((tmp + 1.00 / v2 + 0.78) / 0.23))
    tmp = wp.cos(0.35)
    tmp = ((wp.cos(v2 + 0.79) + wp.cos(tmp + 0.43)) * ((v0 + 0.89 - v1 + 0.71) + (v1 + 0.73 + v0 + 0.51)))
    v1 = (wp.sin(wp.abs(tmp + 0.40)) / (wp.abs(tmp + 0.79) - (v2 + 0.90 + v1 + 0.40)))
    data[tid] = v0
